<p><span class="anchor" id="p66"></span>فَلهُ نصفه نَاقِصا بِلَا خِيَار فان عَابَ<a href="#p66" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p67"></span>أَي صَار ذَا عيب<a href="#p67" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
